Ebola data and statistics - 4 Mar 2015
--------------------------------------
(Data up to 23 Feb 2015 Liberia, and 28 Feb 2015 for Guinea and Sierra Leone)

- Guinea cumulative cases (deaths):
Confirmed cases 2808 (1735)
Probable cases 392 (392)
Suspected 5
Total cases 3205 (2127)
- Liberia cumulative cases (deaths):
Confirmed cases 3153 (not available)
Probable cases 1888 (not available)
Suspected 4224 (not available)
Total cases 9265 (4057)
- Sierra Leone cumulative cases (deaths):
Confirmed cases 8353 (3164)
Probable cases 287 (208)
Suspected 2803 (158)
Total cases 11 443 (3530)
All countries
- Total cases 23 913 (9714)

